    MM2 Local Trade GUI
    Place this LocalScript inside StarterPlayerScripts (or StarterGui)
    
    Based on the game's existing TradeModule, Trade RemoteEvents/Functions,
    and InventoryModule found in the place file.
    
    Features:
        - Send / cancel / accept / decline trade requests
